                            <comment id="14297066" author="garydgregory" created="Thu, 29 Jan 2015 16:10:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The docs are wrong, it was not updated to the latest version of &lt;tt&gt;org.apache.logging.log4j.web.TestAsyncServlet&lt;/tt&gt; (see git).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Just change &lt;tt&gt;Log4jWebLifeCycle&lt;/tt&gt; to &lt;tt&gt;Log4jWebSupport&lt;/tt&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; Log4jWebSupport webLifeCycle =     WebLoggerContextUtils.getWebLifeCycle(TestAsyncServlet.&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.getServletContext());
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Gary&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14297084" author="garydgregory" created="Thu, 29 Jan 2015 16:23:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed docs in git master. Please verify that the new example works for you.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
